@ProductsService.Api_HostAddress = https://localhost:7243

### Health (anonymous)
GET {{ProductsService.Api_HostAddress}}/api/health

### Login
# @name login
POST {{ProductsService.Api_HostAddress}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "P@ssw0rd!"
}

### Create product
POST {{ProductsService.Api_HostAddress}}/api/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}

{
  "name": "Wireless Mouse",
  "colour": "Black",
  "price": 29.99
}

### List all products
GET {{ProductsService.Api_HostAddress}}/api/products
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}

### List products by colour
GET {{ProductsService.Api_HostAddress}}/api/products?colour=Black
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.accessToken}}
